T02TD2059E:155a-1: ha ri ti kunda la dha ra ni s'a dha nam /
T02TD2059E:155a-3: 'phrog ma rna cha 'dzin ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD2059E:155a-6: 'phrog ma rna cha 'dzin ma zhes bya ba aa pa tsha ra'i sgrub thabs la gong bzhin du rtags dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
T02TD2059E:155a-7: ri'i rtse mor nyi ma re la khri phrag re bzlas la nya'i nub mo mtshan phyed kyi dus su 'ong bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2059E:155a-8: de nas 'dis nor 'bum phrag re ster ro //
T02TD2059E:155a-9: rgyab tu khur nas gling bzhi ston par byed do //
T02TD2059E:155a-10: bcud la sogs pa ster ro //
T02TD2059E:155a-11: rna cha 'dzin pa'i aa pa tsha ri'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
